{"tid":2494833,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"好爸爸工作猝死 七口之家失依靠","createTime":"2021-04-18T22:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T23:46:44.000Z","uid":10199,"like":7,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"861cfec061ec0a9d8ea5cebba33cc7b1efe3a25a","tid":2494833,"uid":10199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20210419/s00046/fdf97898aeb24d312d00554d40eddace.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20210419%2Fs00046%2Ffdf97898aeb24d312d00554d40eddace.jpg&h=7eb96dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【明報專訊】300平方呎單位內縈繞着佛經機聲響與稚童的嚎啕大哭，老婦的悲泣在屋外走廊迴盪，蓋過少婦無助的啜泣。三子之父譚雙貴獨力挑起養活一家七口的擔子，惜日前在貨櫃碼頭工作時猝斃，遺下年邁父母、妻子及3個稚子，全家現靠8萬元積蓄過活。這個好爸爸生前再忙再累，亦會與兒子們玩「大富翁」，年僅9歲的長子相信爸爸會復活，「我會讀好書，發明一隻藥救番爸爸」，他堅定地如是說。<br />\n<br />\n明報記者 黃詩雅<br />\n<br />\n37歲的譚雙貴任職倉務員10年，與30歲妻子周潔、3個兒子、父母共一家七口居於天水圍一個約300呎的單位，疫情下原從事屋邨維修的譚父失業，月入約兩萬元的譚雙貴成全家唯一經濟支柱。譚雙貴在葵青貨櫃碼頭工作，與另一同事24小時輪班工作，隨着次子及孻子出生，加上父親近月失業，為了掙取更多日薪，譚減少放假或回家休息，「試過最長第五日先返嚟，一星期見得兩日」。譚妻說。<br />\n<br />\n老父疫下失業 減放假盼多掙<br />\n<br />\n本月9日，譚在貨櫃碼頭乘車前往工作位置期間暈倒，同事為他急救並召救護車，惜終返魂乏術。譚太接獲丈夫同事通知，帶同3稚子趕赴仁濟醫院，惟未能見到丈夫最後一面。譚的死因仍待法醫檢驗，初步懷疑涉心臟問題，譚太說，丈夫無高血壓，但近年有胸口痛，每次痛楚持續數秒，他定期到屯門醫院普通科門診覆診，但毋須服藥，「做過心電圖、驗血，檢查過好多嘢話佢無問題」。<br />\n<br />\n妻：佢幾辛苦都陪3個兒子玩<br />\n<br />\n「佢幾辛苦都好，佢都幫我照顧（小孩），幫我一齊分擔，佢之前唔識斬雞，𠵱家都識幫我斬雞，幫我洗衫，有時見到我攰幫我拖地」，譚太到貴州工作時邂逅丈夫，兩人結婚十一載，譚太一直與家姑在家照顧小孩。「佢一直都話辛苦，佢想轉工，但係因為有色盲，好多嘢佢做唔到，佢想陪小朋友多啲，因為佢𠵱家呢份工好少時間陪伴屋企人。」縱然工作再忙再累，譚生前仍會把握公餘時間與兒子玩「大富翁」、「璀璨寶石」等桌遊及到處遊玩，「4月5號佢攞假陪小朋友去沙灘玩，去馬灣」，譚太說着潸然淚下，不敢回想當日一家共享天倫之樂的時光。<br />\n<br />\n訪問期間，譚老太帶兩歲孫兒到走廊玩耍，卻禁不住嚎哭，「如果你攞綜援你就唔使走啦，我都嗌你攞綜援，咁辛苦」。譚太說，「佢（丈夫）覺得自己有手有腳，可以養得掂頭家，佢就寧願自己辛苦啲。佢去淘寶買20蚊嘅衫著，但為咗我同小朋友，幾貴嘅衫都捨得買；佢食飯都會揀下午茶嘅時間，留番啲錢畀3個囝囝。」每逢生日、聖誕等節日，譚總會為兒子預備禮物。<br />\n<br />\n9歲長子盼讀好書發明復活藥<br />\n<br />\n9歲的長子說，會照顧母親、兩個弟弟和祖父母，「我會讀好書，發明一隻藥救番爸爸」。譚太形容，長子十分孝順，上次考試更獲全班第一名，「佢都話『媽咪，你堅強啲，其實爸爸係會復活㗎，佢無離開過我哋』」，不過長子現時不願外出，「佢話見到人哋爸爸拖住其他小朋友，就諗起爸爸」；4歲次子亦知道父親離世，變得易發脾氣，終日黏着母親。<br />\n<br />\n譚太一家現靠家翁家姑約8萬元積蓄維持生活，暫無法安排丈夫殮葬事宜。協助譚家的工業傷亡權益會稱，譚雙貴受僱於九龍倉集團的外判公司基懋，已向家屬提供小量應急錢及生活費，具體金額不便透露。"},{"pid":"5b6dc770e12b2c8d1c3c187be6fb288080e6bbc9","tid":2494833,"uid":191815,"like":23,"dislike":4,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:26:53.000Z","msg":"記者最叻就係煽動情緒"},{"pid":"75d276a37864a761ce10b9af4994d3e18a7e671b","tid":2494833,"uid":98994,"like":35,"dislike":7,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:42:29.000Z","msg":"窮又唔戴套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec37f03151147456244439db55b7204649c0d769","tid":2494833,"uid":199771,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:45:35.000Z","msg":"是不是HIT員工？<br />\n誠哥有無恩恤金？"},{"pid":"23461d03c79c8f1150ef4279b437336d72380620","tid":2494833,"uid":352873,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:50:02.000Z","msg":"做倉真係冇發達 做10年ot爆都係2萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6870aa3a8239833c6d1893f60ebaa036e2a45d89","tid":2494833,"uid":149494,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:50:23.000Z","msg":"唔係後生港女<br />\n我地香港人唔撚care"},{"pid":"7ede4bbc2719feef01ef8f88f10737a3dfdcde7e","tid":2494833,"uid":35746,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:53:28.000Z","msg":"成個家庭得8萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72d1ba4c03ce96b5039bdd0dca92290884b2235a","tid":2494833,"uid":290985,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:54:26.000Z","msg":"月入兩萬都生三件<br />\n未生之前都養三個人啦"},{"pid":"5d6649025a65c3c2aaa3a7c502f8d6665318c56e","tid":2494833,"uid":75072,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:55:25.000Z","msg":"窮人生仔。。。"},{"pid":"456424680680154b814328bae7d298554f3865f6","tid":2494833,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nrip"},{"pid":"df2e7bd109064408da2d1bd1d27641093d19cd1f","tid":2494833,"uid":308251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:57:10.000Z","msg":"2萬收入，生3個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6146729206ba53f056a85cbcbb6fc1457bb7c1","tid":2494833,"uid":75050,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:58:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZKNmYHpgzYpZrnZ68eb7awRFHfQwvbMHmyK6jfHMikNJ?filename=sCcTkAS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsCcTkAS.jpg&h=6f1bd39b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ab275a954e855e5584b15cf97f582d490c1b6fb","tid":2494833,"uid":166474,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:58:50.000Z","msg":"一家七口, 咬老綜都多過老公生前份人工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"165b617e3bbb7535aee51f2b22b2081f1e3d7bb7","tid":2494833,"uid":393276,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:59:18.000Z","msg":"又出嚟R錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3554d220da9709b525820bff1505099815aa63","tid":2494833,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T23:01:10.000Z","msg":"佢老豆老母又係好撚無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3567408584f7bd4de56c5a4122bc7329f54c0d3d","tid":2494833,"uid":172172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"861cfec061ec0a9d8ea5cebba33cc7b1efe3a25a","tid":2494833,"uid":10199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20210419/s00046/fdf97898aeb24d312d00554d40eddace.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20210419%2Fs00046%2Ffdf97898aeb24d312d00554d40eddace.jpg&h=7eb96dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【明報專訊】300平方呎單位內縈繞着佛經機聲響與稚童的嚎啕大哭，老婦的悲泣在屋外走廊迴盪，蓋過少婦無助的啜泣。三子之父譚雙貴獨力挑起養活一家七口的擔子，惜日前在貨櫃碼頭工作時猝斃，遺下年邁父母、妻子及3個稚子，全家現靠8萬元積蓄過活。這個好爸爸生前再忙再累，亦會與兒子們玩「大富翁」，年僅9歲的長子相信爸爸會復活，「我會讀好書，發明一隻藥救番爸爸」，他堅定地如是說。<br />\n<br />\n明報記者 黃詩雅<br />\n<br />\n37歲的譚雙貴任職倉務員10年，與30歲妻子周潔、3個兒子、父母共一家七口居於天水圍一個約300呎的單位，疫情下原從事屋邨維修的譚父失業，月入約兩萬元的譚雙貴成全家唯一經濟支柱。譚雙貴在葵青貨櫃碼頭工作，與另一同事24小時輪班工作，隨着次子及孻子出生，加上父親近月失業，為了掙取更多日薪，譚減少放假或回家休息，「試過最長第五日先返嚟，一星期見得兩日」。譚妻說。<br />\n<br />\n老父疫下失業 減放假盼多掙<br />\n<br />\n本月9日，譚在貨櫃碼頭乘車前往工作位置期間暈倒，同事為他急救並召救護車，惜終返魂乏術。譚太接獲丈夫同事通知，帶同3稚子趕赴仁濟醫院，惟未能見到丈夫最後一面。譚的死因仍待法醫檢驗，初步懷疑涉心臟問題，譚太說，丈夫無高血壓，但近年有胸口痛，每次痛楚持續數秒，他定期到屯門醫院普通科門診覆診，但毋須服藥，「做過心電圖、驗血，檢查過好多嘢話佢無問題」。<br />\n<br />\n妻：佢幾辛苦都陪3個兒子玩<br />\n<br />\n「佢幾辛苦都好，佢都幫我照顧（小孩），幫我一齊分擔，佢之前唔識斬雞，𠵱家都識幫我斬雞，幫我洗衫，有時見到我攰幫我拖地」，譚太到貴州工作時邂逅丈夫，兩人結婚十一載，譚太一直與家姑在家照顧小孩。「佢一直都話辛苦，佢想轉工，但係因為有色盲，好多嘢佢做唔到，佢想陪小朋友多啲，因為佢𠵱家呢份工好少時間陪伴屋企人。」縱然工作再忙再累，譚生前仍會把握公餘時間與兒子玩「大富翁」、「璀璨寶石」等桌遊及到處遊玩，「4月5號佢攞假陪小朋友去沙灘玩，去馬灣」，譚太說着潸然淚下，不敢回想當日一家共享天倫之樂的時光。<br />\n<br />\n訪問期間，譚老太帶兩歲孫兒到走廊玩耍，卻禁不住嚎哭，「如果你攞綜援你就唔使走啦，我都嗌你攞綜援，咁辛苦」。譚太說，「佢（丈夫）覺得自己有手有腳，可以養得掂頭家，佢就寧願自己辛苦啲。佢去淘寶買20蚊嘅衫著，但為咗我同小朋友，幾貴嘅衫都捨得買；佢食飯都會揀下午茶嘅時間，留番啲錢畀3個囝囝。」每逢生日、聖誕等節日，譚總會為兒子預備禮物。<br />\n<br />\n9歲長子盼讀好書發明復活藥<br />\n<br />\n9歲的長子說，會照顧母親、兩個弟弟和祖父母，「我會讀好書，發明一隻藥救番爸爸」。譚太形容，長子十分孝順，上次考試更獲全班第一名，「佢都話『媽咪，你堅強啲，其實爸爸係會復活㗎，佢無離開過我哋』」，不過長子現時不願外出，「佢話見到人哋爸爸拖住其他小朋友，就諗起爸爸」；4歲次子亦知道父親離世，變得易發脾氣，終日黏着母親。<br />\n<br />\n譚太一家現靠家翁家姑約8萬元積蓄維持生活，暫無法安排丈夫殮葬事宜。協助譚家的工業傷亡權益會稱，譚雙貴受僱於九龍倉集團的外判公司基懋，已向家屬提供小量應急錢及生活費，具體金額不便透露。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T23:08:48.000Z","msg":"譚太說，丈夫無高血壓，但近年有胸口痛，每次痛楚持續數秒，他定期到屯門醫院普通科門診覆診，但毋須服藥，「做過心電圖、驗血，檢查過好多嘢話佢無問題」。<br />\n<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cffa70dfdbcb407ecfe9ce0909fd8d8c2c5b0d95","tid":2494833,"uid":289115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T23:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c99ca305c5b22eb724841cdb798a98d56ec4479","tid":2494833,"uid":309558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T23:11:22.000Z","msg":"黃定藍?"},{"pid":"26b90fa5f21695ce2ade1164beee87f59e841e0e","tid":2494833,"uid":325346,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T23:13:12.000Z","msg":"戴套啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留下三個遺孤<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無錢就去兒童之家啦"},{"pid":"98d0abbbe8915bfd4dd17c2b318211a3ce45600a","tid":2494833,"uid":262200,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T23:14:35.000Z","msg":"點L解要生咁多件<br />\n真係覺得自己養得起?????"},{"pid":"1607ff7a289c42a59366a869ffe85edfaa801839","tid":2494833,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75d276a37864a761ce10b9af4994d3e18a7e671b","tid":2494833,"uid":98994,"like":35,"dislike":7,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:42:29.000Z","msg":"窮又唔戴套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T23:17:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">蝗族日常：&quot;你估我想架？？冇錢落袋呀！！！&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(BTW，一早屌日月毒果都係落藥維撚潛党報！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3cdf1c87d47b144547689f1bd6147d174a81813f","tid":2494833,"uid":124585,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTi